node.text: Back to basic comfort food, teochew porridge with leftover chap chye (mixed veggie stew) and steam barramundi with garlic and fermented black beans. Sio sio cheng cheng, simple and satisfying lunch. #teochewporridge #chapchye #barramundi #porridge #homecooking #stayhomesg #circuitbreaker #singaporehomecooks #sgeats #sgfood #stfoodtrending #8dayseat #burpplesg #sgfoodies #chinesefood #huffposttaste #foodgram #buzzfeedfood #eattheworld #thekitchn #feedfeed #f52grams #heresmyfood #sghomecooking #foodphotography #beautifulcuisines #foodstagram #foodgawker #foodspotting #kuhlbarra
I like simple comfort dishes. So good for rainy day!
